channel.title: Moparscape webclient
channel.description:
im not sure if this is the best place to post this, but i have to start somewhere.
ive seen alot of members, even seniour members have big trouble with making webcliets.
there are a few people helping, people like javafire and ric, but its not enough.
i just realised that moparscape has its own webclient, so i thought we can ask moparscape itself to give us its webclient, eventualy it will be modefied to the extant of downloadeble clients.
i know this idea might not seem so bright, but it could be worth a try.
im sorry for any spelling mistakes, im russian. i could just use spell check, but im not afraid to let people know that i misspell (other people die of embaresment on every small thing, example: omfg a pimple!!@!#!@ im not going to school, lol)
